Sinnertwin growled, and stopped emiting flame from his mouths, as some of
the machine gun bullets had made it past the flame, without melting, and
chipped his teeth, so he growled in pain, but kept his flame cannon on his
back shooting, "We burn Autobot" said one of the heads in fury, as he moved
forward towards Symphony, still shooting the flames, "We rip Autobot" said
the other head, as it lunged in for a bite.
